{
  "texts": [
    "The system needs to respond quickly to requests to ensure effective performance.",
    "Patient EMRs can be large in size.",
    "As a blockchain grows in size, its scalability decreases.",
    "Therefore, in the proposed scheme, the data are stored in a document-oriented database instead of a blockchain.",
    "The blockchain is used only to store cryptographic digests of data for access control purposes."
  ]
}